-- Clean Course Topics HTML (catalog_product_entity_text, attribute_id 72 = description).
--
-- One-time normalisation of the "Course Details" tab markup for the
-- 1144 standard-pattern course descriptions. Each topic header
-- (a paragraph whose whole content is a strong run) becomes an h3 with class
-- course-topic-h3; all sub-topic content becomes ul/li bullets; every non-allowed
-- tag (span, div, a, code, script, img, ...) is stripped. The cleaned values use
-- only the h3, ul, li and i tags.
--
-- Generated by scripts/local-dev/clean-course-topics.php — do not hand-edit.
-- Each UPDATE is guarded by MD5(value): a row is only rewritten while its
-- content still matches what was cleaned, so this is idempotent and will not
-- clobber a course description edited after this migration was generated.
--
-- Irregular rows (a strong run used outside the topic-header pattern) were
-- intentionally left untouched for manual review.

